{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MIME type","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/MIME_type","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>MIME 類型</strong> (現在被更準確的稱作「媒體類型」（media type），但有時也被稱作「内容類型」（content type）) 是一種隨附文件發送的標識字符串。它主要用於標示文件類型、描述內容的類型：例如說，一個聲音文件就可能標為<code>audio/ogg</code>、或者圖像檔案就可能是 <code>image/png</code>。</p>\n<p>它的目的與 Microsoft Windows 的副檔名相似。裡面的名字，是源自最初用於 E-Mail 的 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/mime\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">MIME (en-US)</a> 標準。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基礎知識","title":"基礎知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_media_type\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Internet media type</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/media-types.xhtml\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MIME 類型列表</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/Server-side/Configuring_server_MIME_types\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">正確的伺服器 MIME 類型配置 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/MIME_types\">MIME 類型</a>在網頁文本中的詳細用法</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Basics_of_HTTP/MIME_types/Common_types\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Incomplete list of MIME types (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Mozilla/How_Mozilla_determines_MIME_Types\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Mozilla 如何決定 MIME 類型</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaRecorder/mimeType\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Media